components.name: Newsletter
Contact Form

children.attributes:
{
  value: name,
  type: 'text',
  placeholder: 'Name',
	error: showErrors && getError('name'),
  onChange: (value) => setName(value)
}

{
  value: email,
  type: 'email',
  placeholder: 'Email',
	error: showErrors && getError('email'),
  onChange: (value) => setEmail(value)
}

{
  value: message,
  type: 'textarea',
  placeholder: 'Message',
	error: showErrors && getError('message'),
  onChange: (value) => setMessage(value)
}

{
	parentColor: props.parentColor,
  size: "medium",
  state: props.status && 
    props.status.type === "pending" ?
      'loading' : 'normal'
}

components.name: Sign Up Section
Auth

children.attributes:
{
  value: email,
  type: 'email',
  placeholder: 'Email',
	error: showErrors && getError('email'),
  onChange: (value) => setEmail(value)
}

{
  value: pass,
  type: 'password',
  placeholder: 'Password',
	error: showErrors && getError('pass'),
  onChange: (value) => setPass(value)
}

{
  value: confirmPass,
  type: 'password',
  placeholder: 'Confirm Password',
	error: showErrors && getError('confirmPass'),
  onChange: (value) => setConfirmPass(value)
}

{
	parentColor: props.parentColor,
  size: "medium",
  fullWidth: true,
  state: props.status && 
    			props.status.type === "pending" ?
						'loading' : 'normal'
}
